<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-canvaspixelarray.xml">CanvasPixelArray</db:link> object provides ordered, indexed access to the color components of each pixel of the image data. The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-canvaspixelarray.xml">CanvasPixelArray</db:link> can be accessed as normal Javascript array.</db:para>
