<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-canvaspixelarray.xml">CanvasPixelArray</db:link> object represents h×w×4 integers which w and h comes from <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-canvasimagedata.xml">CanvasImageData</db:link>. The length attribute of a <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-canvaspixelarray.xml">CanvasPixelArray</db:link> object must return this h×w×4 number value. This property is read only.</db:para>
